# AI-Powered Maintenance Work Order Automation System

## Overview

This project demonstrates an AI-powered maintenance request automation workflow built with Make.com and Google Workspace.

The system automatically processes maintenance requests submitted through Google Forms, generates a unique Work Order ID, uses AI to classify the issue, assigns the appropriate maintenance team, determines the priority, updates a centralized Google Sheet, and sends notifications through Gmail and Telegram.

---

## Features

- AI-powered maintenance analysis
- Automatic Work Order ID generation
- Intelligent priority assignment
- Automatic maintenance team assignment
- AI-generated maintenance summary
- Google Sheets database update
- Reporter acknowledgement email
- Maintenance notification email
- Telegram alerts
- Priority-based workflow routing

---

## Workflow

```text
Google Form
      │
Google Sheets
      │
Generate Work Order ID
      │
Reporter Acknowledgement Email
      │
AI Analysis
      │
Parse JSON
      │
Priority Router
      ├── Critical
      ├── High
      └── Medium
      │
Update Google Sheet
      │
Telegram Notification
      │
Maintenance Email
```
